<section class="pt-9 pb-2 py-md-10 bg-stone" id="quote" style="background-image: url(/img/background/avator-bg.png);">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title justify-content-center mb-2 mb-md-8 wow fadeInUp">
                <span class="shape shape-left bg-danger"></span>
                <h2 class="text-white">What Do Kidneys Do?</h2>
                <span class="shape shape-right bg-danger"></span>
            </div>

            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Most people have two kidneys and they are located in your lower back. Your kidneys filter your blood, regulate blood pressure, and regulate several key nutrients such as calcium, phosphate, and potassium. If someone's kidneys do not work properly or are injured in some way that person can developer <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/kidney-disease/" class="text-danger">Chronic Kidney Disease</a> which is often abbreviated to CKD.                    
                </p>

                <p class="mb-0">
                    You can find out more about what the kidneys do <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/Kidneyhealth/Documents/kidney%20guide.pdf" class="text-danger" target="_blank">in this booklet</a> from the NHS and Kidney Research UK or on <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/Kidneyhealth/Documents/kidney%20guide.pdf" class="text-danger" target="_blank">this page</a> from the National Kidney Foundation.
                </p>
            </blockquote>
            
            <br /><br /><br /><br />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

